\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 Project Goal\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Create the primary entry point into an interactive learning ecosystem for university students.\
This is NOT a course menu.\
This is NOT a flowchart.\
This is NOT a game map.\
It should feel like the opening page of an explorer's journal where students are invited to discover a living world.\
The emotional experience should be:\
\'95 Wonder\
\'95 Curiosity\
\'95 Possibility\
\'95 Discovery\
\'95 Calm\
\'95 Adventure\
Students should feel invited\'97not instructed.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 Overall Style\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 The island should resemble a hand-painted natural ecosystem.\
Visual inspiration:\
\'95 National Park visitor maps\
\'95 Scientific field guides\
\'95 Expedition journals\
\'95 Ecological illustrations\
\'95 Botanical artwork\
\'95 Tolkien-style landscape painting\
\'95 Beautiful fantasy atlas artwork\
Avoid:\
\'95 Cartoon style\
\'95 Children's book styling\
\'95 Video game maps\
\'95 Corporate infographics\
\'95 Flat icon design\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0

