\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 Interactive Design\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Every habitat.\
Every value.\
Every landmark.\
Every trailhead.\
Should be individually clickable.\
Clickable areas should be invisible until hovered.\
Hover effect:\
Soft golden glow.\
Slight enlargement.\
Subtle animated pulse.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa321\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 Overall Feeling\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 This should not feel like opening an online course.\
It should feel like unfolding an explorer's map before beginning an unforgettable expedition.\
Students should spend several minutes simply exploring the island before clicking anything.\
The image itself should invite curiosity.\
The island should communicate one central idea before a single word is read:\
"There is always another place to discover."\
